Compare","rank":0,"dataSourceName":"","displayRows":50,"dependencies":[1,2],"options":{},"className":"com.datagaps.dataflow.models.DataCompareComponent","isCheckpointEnabled":"N","executionOption":"allparentpassorfail","excludeNotification":"N"},{"partitionOptions":{"partitionType":"","name":""},"easyQueryDefJson":{"sqlQuery":""},"componentId":5,"componentName":"Transformation","tableName":"Transformation","category":"Processor","componentType":"SQL","rank":0,"dataSourceName":"","displayRows":50,"dependencies":[2],"options":{"dbTable":"SELECT
    -- pass-through / cleaned base columns
    s.sno,
    s.months_as_customer,
    s.age,
    s.policy_number,
    s.policy_state,
    s.policy_csl,
    s.policy_deductable,
    s.policy_annual_premium,
    s.umbrella_limit,
    s.insured_zip,
    s.insured_sex,
    s.insured_education_level,
    s.insured_occupation,
    s.insured_hobbies,
    s.insured_relationship,
    s.capital_gains,
    s.capital_loss,
    s.policy_bind_date,
    s.incident_date,
    s.incident_state,
    s.incident_type,
    s.collision_type,
    s.incident_severity,
    s.authorities_contacted,
    s.incident_city,
    s.incident_location,
    s.incident_hour_of_the_day,
    s.number_of_vehicles_involved,
    s.property_damage,
    s.bodily_injuries,
    s.witnesses,
    s.police_report_available,
    s.total_claim_amount,
    s.injury_claim,
    s.property_claim,
    s.vehicle_claim,
    s.auto_make,
    s.auto_model,
    s.auto_year,
    s.fraud_reported,

    CASE
        WHEN s.age < 25 THEN 'YOUNG'
        WHEN s.age BETWEEN 25 AND 50 THEN 'ADULT'
        ELSE 'SENIOR'
    END AS age_group,

    CASE
        WHEN s.policy_annual_premium < 600 THEN 'LOW'
        WHEN s.policy_annual_premium BETWEEN 600 AND 1200 THEN 'MID'
        ELSE 'HIGH'
    END AS premium_bucket,

    CASE
        WHEN s.months_as_customer < 12 THEN 'NEW'
        WHEN s.months_as_customer BETWEEN 12 AND 60 THEN 'LOYAL'
        ELSE 'VETERAN'
    END AS customer_tenure_cat,

    (COALESCE(s.injury_claim,0) * 0.4) +
    (COALESCE(s.property_claim,0) * 0.2) +
    (COALESCE(s.vehicle_claim,0) * 0.4) AS claim_severity_score,

    (COALESCE(s.injury_claim,0) + COALESCE(s.property_claim,0) + COALESCE(s.vehicle_claim,0))
        AS total_claim_verified,

    CASE
        WHEN COALESCE(s.witnesses,0) = 0 AND COALESCE(s.bodily_injuries,0) > 0 THEN 1
        WHEN s.authorities_contacted = 'NONE' AND s.incident_severity = 'MAJOR DAMAGE' THEN 1
        WHEN s.insured_occupation IN ('UNEMPLOYED','SELF-EMPLOYED') THEN 1
        ELSE 0
    END AS high_risk_flag

FROM (

    SELECT
        sno,
        months_as_customer,
        age,
        policy_number,

        UPPER(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(policy_state, ''), ' '), 'NA'), '?')) AS policy_state,
        UPPER(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(policy_csl, ''), ' '), 'NA'), '?')) AS policy_csl,

        policy_deductable,
        policy_annual_premium,
        umbrella_limit,
        insured_zip,

        UPPER(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(insured_sex, ''), ' '), 'NA'), '?')) AS insured_sex,
        UPPER(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(insured_education_level, ''), ' '), 'NA'), '?')) AS insured_education_level,
        UPPER(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(insured_occupation, ''), ' '), 'NA'), '?')) AS insured_occupation,
        UPPER(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(insured_hobbies, ''), ' '), 'NA'), '?')) AS insured_hobbies,
        UPPER(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(insured_relationship, ''), ' '), 'NA'), '?')) AS insured_relationship,

        capital_gains,
        capital_loss,

        
        policy_bind_date,

        incident_date,

        UPPER(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(incident_state, ''), ' '), 'NA'), '?')) AS incident_state,
        UPPER(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(incident_type, ''), ' '), 'NA'), '?')) AS incident_type,
        UPPER(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(collision_type, ''), ' '), 'NA'), '?')) AS collision_type,
        UPPER(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(incident_severity, ''), ' '), 'NA'), '?')) AS incident_severity,
        UPPER(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(authorities_contacted, ''), ' '), 'NA'), '?')) AS authorities_contacted,
        UPPER(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(incident_city, ''), ' '), 'NA'), '?')) AS incident_city,
        UPPER(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(incident_location, ''), ' '), 'NA'), '?')) AS incident_location,

        incident_hour_of_the_day,
        number_of_vehicles_involved,

        UPPER(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(property_damage, ''), ' '), 'NA'), '?')) AS property_damage,

        bodily_injuries,
        witnesses,
        UPPER(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(police_report_available, ''), ' '), 'NA'), '?')) AS police_report_available,

        total_claim_amount,
        injury_claim,
        property_claim,
        vehicle_claim,

        UPPER(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(auto_make, ''), ' '), 'NA'), '?')) AS auto_make,
        UPPER(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(auto_model, ''), ' '), 'NA'), '?')) AS auto_model,
        auto_year,

        UPPER(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(NULLIF(fraud_reported, ''), ' '), 'NA'), '?')) AS fraud_reported

    FROM Staging_Layer
